Juliana Harkavy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Juliana_Harkavy 0 Juliana Jay Harkavy (born January 1, 1985) is an American actress. She is known for portraying Rebecca in Dolphin Tale, Jessie in To Write Love on her Arms, and Alisha in the television series The Walking Dead. Her roles include a starring role in the horror film Last Shift, and a reprise of her role as Rebecca in Dolphin Tale 2. She is currently a series regular on The CW superhero series Arrow, portraying Dinah Drake / Black Canary. Juliana_Jay_Harkavy ( born January_1_,_1985 ) is an_American_actress .
